name: CI Global Real Asset Private Pool
longDescription: The CI Global Real Asset Private Pool (the Fund) seeks to provide regular income and capital appreciation. The Fund investing primarily in companies with direct or indirect exposure to real assets, such as infrastructure and residential and commercial real estate, located anywhere in the world.
